at Belle Isle, Fletch.

01:21:56.311 --> 01:22:00.509
After you die, who's gonna prove that
you did not sell your land to Everest?

01:22:00.582 --> 01:22:03.278
You may have this town
in your back pocket, Johnson,

01:22:03.351 --> 01:22:06.320
but there are a lot of people downstairs
who are gonna be very interested...

01:22:06.388 --> 01:22:09.846
in the hows and whys
of Amanda Ray's death.

01:22:09.925 --> 01:22:11.950
She knew about Bluebird.

01:22:12.027 --> 01:22:14.860
She started a file on you,
and you found out about it.

01:22:14.930 --> 01:22:20.197
That was my lucky night. The night I found
the Bluebird file, the night you porked her.

01:22:20.268 --> 01:22:24.728
I figured it was like an alligator shoot on
the freeway, if you'll excuse the metaphor.

01:22:24.806 --> 01:22:28.537
- It's not a metaphor. It's a simile, to be precise.
- Whatever.

01:22:28.610 --> 01:22:34.412
So you poisoned Amanda, figuring I'd sell
and get out if I was facing a murder charge.

01:22:34.482 --> 01:22:38.111
- I don't scare easy. I'm too dumb.
- So it would seem.

01:22:38.186 --> 01:22:42.247
Now get out of my mama's chair before
I put the first bullet up your nose.

01:22:42.324 --> 01:22:44.656
Are you kidding?

01:22:44.726 --> 01:22:47.456
You pull that trigger and 100
people will be up here in a second.

01:22:47.529 --> 01:22:50.464
My dear boy, why would
I do my own dirty work?

01:22:51.967 --> 01:22:55.232
Those hundred do-gooders down
there dressed in rebel crap...

01:22:55.303 --> 01:22:57.737
will be my alibi.

01:22:59.040 --> 01:23:01.873
Now get outta
my mama's chair!

01:23:01.943 --> 01:23:05.538
I synchronized my beloved Laker
watch with Miss Culpepper's Timex.

01:23:05.613 --> 01:23:08.878
If I don’t join her at the ministry
in 10 minutes, the whole ugly story...

01:23:08.950 --> 01:23:11.748
goes out on
the Farnsworth Network.

01:23:11.820 --> 01:23:13.913
Of course, it's cable, but...

01:23:13.989 --> 01:23:16.389
- You're bluffing, Fletch.
- No, I'm not.

01:23:16.458 --> 01:23:19.359
You think you're not...
but you are.

01:23:21.029 --> 01:23:23.463
Swell.

01:23:25.000 --> 01:23:29.869
- Did he hurt you?
- Not yet. That comes later.

01:23:29.938 --> 01:23:31.906
Sorry, Becky.

01:23:31.973 --> 01:23:36.967
The band won't take a break for some
time, so screaming would be futile.

01:23:37.045 --> 01:23:40.014
Mr. Fletch's convenient
appearance has allowed us...

01:23:40.081 --> 01:23:45.451
to move up our plans for your
demise to coincide with his.

01:23:45.520 --> 01:23:50.321
Now I'm goin' downstairs
to be the gracious host.

01:23:50.392 --> 01:23:54.158
Do what you have to do.

01:23:54.229 --> 01:23:57.357
- The bride of Frankenstein.
- Put my mama down!

01:23:57.432 --> 01:23:59.423
Oh! I'm sorry.

01:23:59.501 --> 01:24:01.935
Oh, how clumsy of me.

01:24:02.003 --> 01:24:05.769
Oops! I'm sorry. I stepped
right on her mustache.

01:24:05.840 --> 01:24:09.139
Get away! Get away!

01:24:09.210 --> 01:24:12.111
- Sorry. I was just trying to help.
- It's all right, Mama.

01:24:12.180 --> 01:24:14.444
You should be more careful
where you put your breakables.

01:24:14.516 --> 01:24:16.984
I've been careful
all my life.

01:24:17.052 --> 01:24:19.213
When she was sick,
I was careful.

01:24:19.287 --> 01:24:23.621
Then that goddamn Jimmy Lee's
ministry... taking everything she had.

01:24:23.691 --> 01:24:26.785
Bloodsuckers!

01:24:26.861 --> 01:24:30.627
It's gonna be all right, Mama.
And when we're far, far away...

01:24:30.698 --> 01:24:32.757
from this godforsaken
chemical swamp,

01:24:32.834 --> 01:24:37.635
we're gonna sit back and
watch 'em all just decompose.

01:24:37.705 --> 01:24:41.698
That should be good for Bibleland's business,
all their customers glowing in the dark.

01:24:41.776 --> 01:24:44.745
I hope they all fry
in hell!

01:24:44.813 --> 01:24:48.146
- You bloodsucking bastards!
- Isn't this interesting?

01:24:48.216 --> 01:24:50.184
- Put that down.
- She really is in there.

01:24:50.251 --> 01:24:52.913
- Put that down.
- She seems to have lost a little weight.

01:24:52.987 --> 01:24:56.184
I thought you had her stuffed and
mounted. Here she is. Head's up!

01:24:56.257 --> 01:24:58.088
Ohh! Ohh!
Becky!

01:25:09.437 --> 01:25:13.874
Swine... Darryl, are
you having a good time?

01:25:58.019 --> 01:26:01.420
Welcome to great Noah's Ark...

01:26:01.489 --> 01:26:05.289
where we have a flood
every 10 minutes.

01:26:07.228 --> 01:26:09.128
In the...

01:26:17.005 --> 01:26:18.632
No! This way.

01:26:18.706 --> 01:26:20.765
Join our pyramid of prayer.

01:26:20.842 --> 01:26:23.333
For only $12,

01:26:23.411 --> 01:26:27.347
you begin your exciting journey
up the pyramid.

01:26:27.415 --> 01:26:29.349
And when you reach the top,

01:26:29.417 --> 01:26:35.481
you're gonna be the target
of 20,000 prayers!

01:26:35.557 --> 01:26:40.358
A lady in Fargo, North Dakota broke the
chain and began a five-day fit of sneezing...

01:26:40.428 --> 01:26:42.623
